<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْبُخَارِيُّ ج٦ص٦١:</span> <span class="c3">{وَإِنْ جَنَحُوا}</span>: طَلَبُوا.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>السِّلْمُ , وَالسَّلْمُ , وَالسَّلَامُ , وَاحِدٌ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
